{"word":"G5483 - χαρίζομαι - charízomai - khar-id'-zom-ahee - Deliver","slug":"G5483","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χαρίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>charízomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khar-id'-zom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Deliver"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C7;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - charizomai</b> - <i>khar-id'-zom-ahee</i><p/>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G5485\">G5485</a>; to grant as a <i>favor</i>, that is, gratuitously, in kindness, pardon or rescue: - deliver, (frankly) forgive, (freely) give, grant."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2168\">G2168</a>, <a href=\"#/G2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G2170\">G2170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5486\">G5486</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487\">G5487</a>, <a href=\"#/G884\">G884</a>"}]}